665
00:29:29,392 --> 00:29:30,226
No.

666
00:29:30,226 --> 00:29:31,102
- Lie to her.

667
00:29:31,103 --> 00:29:33,396
- Nina, I will be right back.

668
00:29:34,481 --> 00:29:35,731
- All right.

669
00:29:35,732 --> 00:29:37,941
(tense music)

670
00:29:37,942 --> 00:29:39,234
- Wait a second.

671
00:29:39,235 --> 00:29:43,322
(rock music)
