784
00:34:09,881 --> 00:34:11,965
and at this very late hour.

785
00:34:11,966 --> 00:34:14,384
- I have a little undercover investigation

786
00:34:14,385 --> 00:34:15,928
that you'd be perfect for.

787
00:34:19,015 --> 00:34:21,099
- Ah, damn soundproof doors.

788
00:34:21,100 --> 00:34:22,225
I can't hear them.

789
00:34:22,226 --> 00:34:24,269
- And you'll be well compensated.

790
00:34:24,270 --> 00:34:26,396
I'm not like Sandra.

791
00:34:26,397 --> 00:34:30,525
- I haven't had any problems
lately with my cash flow.

792
00:34:30,526 --> 00:34:32,235
- You're very lucky.

793
00:34:32,236 --> 00:34:33,487
Money is very important,

794
00:34:33,488 --> 00:34:35,280
but it's not the answer to everything.

795
00:34:35,281 --> 00:34:37,365
Love makes all things possible.

796
00:34:37,366 --> 00:34:41,495
So I'm willing to pay you
in nookie certificates.

797
00:34:41,496 --> 00:34:43,038
- Really?

798
00:34:43,039 --> 00:34:46,291
Then why don't we stop at
the hotel bar for a cocktail

799
00:34:46,292 --> 00:34:48,794
and start this assignment off right?

800
00:34:48,795 --> 00:34:50,545
- You read my mind.

801
00:34:50,546 --> 00:34:52,714
(Kaori growling)

802
00:34:52,715 --> 00:34:54,091
Hi, Kaori.

803
00:34:54,092 --> 00:34:56,134
- Sleeping with the enemy?

804
00:34:56,135 --> 00:34:57,469
Traitor!

805
00:34:57,470 --> 00:35:00,138
(hammer banging)

806
00:35:00,139 --> 00:35:02,724
- I just remembered I
